INSERT INTO `FBNOTES` VALUES (17,3,'Serial Number',22,25,130,40,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','The letters and numbers of the serial number are in an orderly row.','The numbers and letters in the serial number are not in one line and seemed to \"dance\". '),(17,1,'Portrait',148,17,255,138,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'5096o1p1.jpg','5096f1p1.jpg','1. The portrait is with a slightly brighter image. \r%NL%2. The beard and the hair are more grizzled.\r%NL%3. The eyebrows look any different than those of the counterfeit.\r%NL%4. On the left the eyelashes are brighter. ','1. The portrait has a more contrasting and darker image.\r%NL%2. In the beard and hair to the left temple and its base there are darker hairs.\r%NL%3. The right eyebrow looks more scowling, and the left one has a sharper contraction to the nose.\r%NL%4. The eyelashes on the left eye are darker. '),(17,2,'Bowtie',147,140,253,160,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'5096o1p2.jpg','5096f1p2.jpg','1. The shadow of the bow tie is brighter and seems to ends in the middle.\r%NL%2. The parallel lines are clear and distinct.\r%NL%','1.The shadow of the bow tie is darker.\r%NL%2. The parallel lines at the top corner of the shirt next to the lapel merge and form a dark spot.\r%NL%'),(17,4,'Watermark',372,56,430,128,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'5096o1p3.jpg','5096f1p3.jpg','* A halftone image of the portrait of the banknote','The watermark of the super-forgery from the end of 2001 clearly differs from that of the original banknote:\r%NL%* missing the halftone and the image volume typical for the original;\r%NL%* the features of the portrait of the watermark in the counterfeit differ from those of the visible portrait of the banknote instead of having full accordance, as in the original;\r%NL%\r%NL%<!>  Good detection was obtained when compared to an original banknote.'),(18,11,'Letter S',416,160,442,171,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1h96o1p2.jpg','1h96f1p3.jpg','The same element in the original banknote is more slanting.','The upper part of letter \"S\" ends in a much sharper angle than the original.'),(18,5,'Optically Variable Ink',363,133,425,159,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1h96o1p3.jpg','1h96f1p4.jpg','The number has a relief.','The number has no relief, OVI is good,\r but easily erase, and then the color of \"100\" is not changed. When viewing at a different angle the color of the number changes, as in the original.'),(18,2,'Security thread',98,1,106,176,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1h96o2p1.jpg','1h96f2p1.jpg','Repeating positive inscription \"100 USA\".','In some counterfeits the thread is relatively good, and the differences are only visible with a good zoom. The digits of the number \'100\' and the letters \'USA\' have larger distances between them. \r%NL%In the counterfeit letters are unclear, paler, less focus. In some counterfeits the thread looks as if detached inside the paper. In other under UV light the thread does not reflect as intensely as in the original banknotes.'),(18,3,'Watermark',380,59,430,130,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1h96o2p2.jpg','1h96f2p2.jpg','A halftone image of the portrait from the banknote.','The watermark is slightly imitated and does not differ, as the image is printed with some sort of fat. In others the watermark has sharp edges. Missing halftones and image volume.\r%NL%\r%NL%<!>The feature is not very secure because in the originals also are found many varieties. Good identification is obtained by presence of an original in comparison with the test banknote.'),(18,4,'Ornaments',432,135,455,162,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1h96o2p3.jpg','1h96f2p3.jpg','The second bottom up leaf in the ornamentation the inside is white. ','The contours of the leaf block the white spot between them.'),(18,6,'Base of the tower',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,214,72,232,92,'1h96o2p4.jpg','1h96f2p4.jpg','The last two sticks in the railing painted with vertical bars are intersected by a short horizontal dash.','The horizontal dash is missing.'),(18,8,'Tower',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,218,54,246,68,'1h96o2p5.jpg','1h96f2p5.jpg','Under the middle window of the tower on the left, there are two lines that turn at right angles. In the upper line the curve is interrupted , as if it has been deleted.\r%NL%In some copyes also the lines are more smudgy and unclear.','The lines are clearly delineated from end to end, clearer and more contrastive.'),(18,9,'Top of the tower',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,226,26,243,49,'1h96o2p6.jpg','1h96f2p6.jpg','The line outlining the left top of the tower of \" Independence Hall\" is weaker and thinner, even in a single area  directly is missing.','The line is clearly outlined and visible end-to-end.'),(18,10,'Stamp of the Treasury',317,63,371,116,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1h96o2p7.jpg','1h96f1p2.jpg','Stamp of the Treasury\r%NL%=======================\r%NL%The elements of the image of the green stamp:\r%NL%a) the tops of the stars are well outlined;\r%NL%b) the contours of the elements are clearly formed. ','Stamp of the Treasury\r%NL%=======================\r%NL%The elements of the image of the green stamp:\r%NL%a) the stars are white circles or small dots;\r%NL%b) there are thickenings in the font of the digits in \'1789\';\r%NL%c) as a whole the contours of the elements are not clearly delineated.\r'),(20,1,'Portrait',68,59,186,190,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'10_f1.jpg','01_f1.jpg','Portrait of Alexander Hamilton.','Portrait of George Washington.'),(20,2,'Indication of the nominal value in words',21,225,245,255,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'10_f.jpg','01_f.jpg','The inscription is \"Ten dollars\".','\"One dollar\" instead of \"Ten dollars\".'),(21,1,'Signs of the Federal Reserve',51,59,155,120,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','Correct correspondence between the letter and number of the the Federal Reserve Bank:\r%NL%\r%NL%Branch of the Fed.reserve | Letter | Number |\r%NL%-----------------------------\r%NL%Dallas, TX      |   K |  11  |\r%NL%San Francisco, CA| L |  12  |\r%NL%=============================\r%NL%','There is a discrepancy between the letter and number designation of the Federal Reserve Bank:\r%NL%\r%NL%Dallas - L - 12 '),(22,1,'Watermark',385,53,438,128,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','A halftone image of the portrait of the banknote.','The watermark is imitated - coated with a white substance on the obverse.'),(22,2,'Security thread',104,1,122,175,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','Polymeric, embedded in the paper, a security thread located left of the portrait, with a repeating microtext \"USA 100\" visible from both sides when observing against the light.\r%NL%','The security thread is imitated - adhered in the paper.'),(22,3,'Identifiers',14,127,52,162,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','Letter (from A to R) or a combination of letter (A to H) and a digit (1 to 4) at the lower left corner indicates what position has held the note on the sheet on which was printed. ','Missing the identifiers that indicate what position has held the note on the sheet when was printed.'),(23,1,'Par value',407,145,452,175,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','','The number of the new nominal value is painted over the old one.'),(23,2,'Textual designation',112,158,346,185,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','','Text designation of the nominal value is written incorrectly - fifte instead of fifty.\r%NL%'),(23,3,'Portrait',177,47,284,150,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'usd5093_ .jpg','usd5093_.jpg','Portrait of Grant.','Portrait of Abraham Lincoln.'),(24,3,'Element',15,85,35,103,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','\r%NL%===================\r%NL%Crisp lines which do not merge with one another.','\r%NL%===================\r%NL%One of the lines in the vignettes next to the leaf adjacent to the triangular figure.'),(24,4,'Lip',227,93,250,109,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','\r%NL%====================\r%NL%In the left corner of the lip there is a dash , forming an arc down.','\r%NL%====================\r%NL%The line in the left corner of the mouth, which forms an arc down, is missing.\r%NL%'),(24,5,'Letters',225,166,255,183,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','\r%NL%==================\r%NL%In the original the letter \'E\' has more rounded lines than the counterfeit.','\r%NL%==================\r%NL%The letters \'E\' and \'D\' are touching differently in the counterfeit.\r%NL%'),(24,6,'Letters',298,1,326,16,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','\r%NL%==================\r%NL%The letters are clearly separated.','\r%NL%==================\r%NL%The upper part of the letter \"N\" merges with the upper left part of the letter \"О\".\r%NL%'),(24,7,'Signature',357,133,383,153,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','\r%NL%====================\r%NL%The point over the penultimate letter of the second signature is missing.','\r%NL%====================\r%NL%Over the penultimate letter in the second signature there are dots of ink / contamination/.\r%NL%'),(24,8,'Element',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,43,9,73,28,'','','\r%NL%====================\r%NL%Between 22nd and 23rd vertical bars forming the horinzontal of the upper left corner is a horizontal a dash.','\r%NL%====================\r%NL%There is no horizontal dash between 22nd and 23rd vertical dashes, forming the horizontal of the upper left corner.\r%NL%'),(24,9,'Element',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,9,61,44,88,'','','\r%NL%===================\r%NL%The lines in the first cylinder are clean and well visible.','\r%NL%===================\r%NL%In the first of the cylinders forming hatches between the two curved lines over the number \"100\" in some counterfeits lines are smudgy and unclear.\r%NL%\r%NL%'),(24,10,'Element',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,129,129,153,155,'','','\r%NL%=====================\r%NL%The left horizontal line of the lantern can be observed well.','\r%NL%=====================\r%NL%Over the letter \"E\" in \"ONE\" is missing the left horizontal line of the lantern.\r%NL%'),(24,11,'Element',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,186,128,225,154,'','','\r%NL%====================\r%NL%Both sides of the base of the lantern are identical.','\r%NL%====================\r%NL%Both sides of the base of the lantern are different - on the right basis is noticeable a right angle.'),(24,12,'Element',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,244,125,269,151,'','','\r%NL%====================\r%NL%At the base of the tree there is a dark transverse line.','\r%NL%====================\r%NL%At the base of the tree the transverse line is very pale.'),(24,13,'Security thread',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,359,1,384,178,'','','\r%NL%===================\r%NL%The inscription on the thread is contrasting and well distinguishable. The thread is also well distinguishable.','\r%NL%===================\r%NL%>It is necessary a good increase<\r%NL%---------------------\r%NL%The inscription on the security thread is unclear and if increase the thread is not immediately evident.'),(24,14,'Stamp of the Treasury',314,82,354,124,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','\r%NL%===================\r%NL%The letters \"EA\" from \"TREASURY\" in the peripheral text at the green stamp are separated in their lower part.\r%NL%','\r%NL%==================\r%NL%The letters \"EA\" from \"TREASURY\" from the peripheral text in the green stamp are joined together at the bottom.\r%NL%============================\r%NL%The stars in the seal of the treasury have unclear peaks.\r%NL%'),(24,15,'Inscription',82,16,386,40,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','The inscription is not solid but is formed from a plurality of fine lines.','The inscription \"THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA\" on the front side is dense.\r%NL%There is no fine grid of white rhomboids or parallel lines, which is compulsory for all bills after 1985.'),(24,1,'Element to the nominal value',41,156,76,183,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1h90o2p1.jpg','1h90f2p1.jpg','Clear lines which do not merge to each other.','The two outer lines of the frame around the number of nominal are merging.'),(26,8,'Security thread',264,2,280,223,171,1,182,221,'','','\r%NL%==========================\r%NL%Вградена в хартията лента с негативен микротекст \"БНБ 10\".','\r%NL%===========================\r%NL%На всички фалшиви банкноти липсва вградена осигурителна нишка. На някои банкноти на обратната страна е отпечатана имитация на такава с неясен текст.'),(26,9,'Watermark',345,43,420,133,23,40,92,150,'','','\r%NL%==========================\r%NL%Полутоново изображение на потрета от банкнотата.','%NL%========================\r%NL%Или липсва напълно, или е по-дребен, контрастен. Изработен е чрез отпечтаване с бяло или безцветно мастило на ситопечат. Проявява се във виолетов цвят при осветяване с УВ-светлина.'),(26,10,'Raised Printing for the Visually Impaired',430,215,455,250,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','\r%NL%==========================\r%NL%При опипване се усеща релефното отпечатване на елемента.','\r%NL%===========================\r%NL%Върху знакът за слепи граждани липсва характерният за оригиналните банкноти релеф в печата.'),(26,1,'Holographic stripe',13,1,60,221,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1099o1p1.jpg','1099f1p1.jpg','\r%NL%========================\r%NL%Холограмна лента с редуващи се изображения на земно кълбо и телескоп, на числото \"10\" и текст \"ЛЕВА\", изписан с минишрифт, които променят цвета си при промяна на ъгъла на наблюдение.','\r%NL%========================\r%NL%Холограмната лента е имитирана чрез сребриста ивица с отпечатани в зелен цвят изображения, имитиращи част от съответните холограмни образи, \rкоито не променят цвета си при промяна на ъгъла на наблюдение. Върху холограмата липсва характерния за оригиналните банкноти релеф в печата.'),(26,2,'Microprint',247,25,310,65,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1099o1p2.jpg','1099f1p2.jpg','\r%NL%==========================\r%NL%Microtextът е четлив, фигурите са ясно очертани.','\r%NL%==========================\r%NL%Не са възпроизведени микротекстът с изписани числа \'10\' и сложните геометрични форми.'),(26,3,'Microprint',360,160,420,215,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1099o1p3.jpg','1099f1p3.jpg','\r%NL%==========================\r%NL%Microtextът е ясен и отчетлив.','\r%NL%===========================\r%NL%Microtextът в номинала не е възпроизведен ясно. '),(26,4,'Microprint',80,12,109,35,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1099o1p4.jpg','1099f1p4.jpg','\r%NL%===========================\r%NL%Microtextът е ясен и четлив.','\r%NL%===========================\r%NL%Microtextът в зоните около портрета не е възпроизведен. Липсва характерният за \rоригиналните банкноти фин релеф от дълбокия печат в портрета.'),(26,5,'Microprint',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,181,17,209,45,'1099o1p5.jpg','1099f1p5.jpg','The microtext is legible.','The microtext is quite blurry and unreadable. '),(26,6,'Microprint',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,126,18,154,60,'1099o1p6.jpg','1099f1p6.jpg','\r%NL%=========================\r%NL%Microtextът е ясен и четлив.','\r%NL%==========================\r%NL%Преплетените микротекстови елементи със сложен пъстроцветен рисунък, не са възпроизведени.'),(26,7,'Element',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,295,90,360,150,'1099o1p7.jpg','1099f1p7.jpg','\r%NL%==========================\r%NL%Контурите на фигурите са ясно очертани.','\r%NL%===========================\r%NL%Под лупа се забелязва, че геометричният рисунък в банкнотите не е възпроизведен.'),(27,1,'Security thread',240,0,252,221,154,2,167,223,'','','\r%NL%=========================\r%NL%Embedded into the paper strip with a negative microtext \"БНБ 20\".','\r%NL%==========================\r%NL%In some of counterfeits is missing a security thread. In another type of counterfeits on both sides of the banknote can be seen traces of an image,\r resembling a security thread with inscription \"20 БНБ\", but when considering the banknote against the light is clearly visible the lack of a security thread.'),(27,4,'Microtext',360,160,420,220,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','','\r%NL%=========================\r%NL%The microtext in the nominal is not reproduced. \r%NL%There is missing the typical for the original notes relief in the printing.'),(27,8,'Sign for the visually impaired',430,215,450,250,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','\r%NL%==========================\r%NL%When touching it feels the embossing print of the two points.','\r%NL%===========================\r%NL%There is missing the typical for the original notes relief in the printingover the sign for visualy impaired people.'),(27,9,'See-through register',320,178,350,210,92,175,133,210,'','','\r%NL%=========================\r%NL%When considering against the light is visible the number \rof the nominal.','\r%NL%========================\r%NL%See-through register: Poorly formed because of,\r that the two sides are printed simultaneously.'),(27,2,'Holographic strip',10,2,60,223,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2099o1p1.jpg','2099f1p1.jpg','\r%NL%=========================\r%NL%Holographic strip with alternating images of an eagle, the number \"20\" and the text \"ЛЕВА\" written in mini font that change their color when changing the viewing angle.','\r%NL%=========================\r%NL%Instead of hologram stripe is adhered an ordinary foil over which lack the typical holographic images and stamp. \r%NL%There is missing the relief of the color line, parallel in overlapping holographic metallized strip.'),(27,3,'Microtext',76,9,105,29,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2099o1p2.jpg','2099f1p2.jpg','\r%NL%=========================\r%NL%The microtext is clear and distinct.\r%NL%When palpate it feels the fine relief of the paper.','\r%NL%==========================\r%NL%The microtext left of the portrait is not reproduced. On the portrait is missing the typical for the original notes fine relief in the printing.'),(27,5,'Microtext',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,257,4,317,26,'2099o1p4.jpg','2099f1p4.jpg','\r%NL%============================\r%NL%The microtext is clear and legible.','\r%NL%============================\r%NL%The microtext is not reproduced with written numbers \"20\" and the complex geometric forms.'),(27,6,'Microtext',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,331,178,370,209,'2099o1p5.jpg','2099f1p5.jpg','\r%NL%===========================\r%NL%The microtext is clear and legible.','\r%NL%==========================\r%NL%The microtext from the repetitive number \"20\", interwoven with multicolored drawing, is not reproduced clearly and legibly.'),(27,7,'Watermark',350,34,415,135,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2099o1p6.jpg','2099f1p6.jpg','\r%NL%=========================\r