ears lighter / dashed /. The horizontal\r lines on the pavement to the car are broken.','\r%NL%===================\r%NL%The hatchure under the car to the far right building is darker / with thick and\r solid lines /. The horizontal lines on the pavement next to the car are continuous.'),(29,6,'Element',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,320,111,339,126,'','','','\r%NL%====================\r%NL%The third vault looks whiter than the original.'),(29,7,'Element',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,364,137,388,153,'','','\r%NL%===================\r%NL%The handwritten letters \"по\", indicating the cliche under the bushes in front of the numbers,\rare seen as faint scribbles.','\r%NL%===================\r%NL%Under the bushes in front of the numbers denoting the clich? clearly are noticed the handwritten  letters \"по\".\r%NL%'),(29,8,'Stamp of the Treasury',310,69,360,116,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','\r%NL%===================\r%NL%The letters \"EA\" in \"TREASURY\" are not joined together in its lower part.','\r%NL%===================\r%NL%The letters \"EA\" in \"TREASURY\" are joned together at the bottom\r%NL%===================\r%NL%The asterisks in the seal of the treasury have vague peaks. There are defects in the printing of the scale.'),(37,1,'Planchettes',120,2,151,21,353,33,384,55,'5088o1p1.jpg','5088f1p1.jpg','\r%NL%=========================\r%NL%Planchettes - little green paper discs embedded in the paper.\r%NL%','\r%NL%=========================\r%NL%Planchettes are printed as green dots on the surface of the paper.\r%NL%'),(38,2,'Identifier',61,128,89,148,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','The identifiers indicate the location of the note on the sheet on which it was printed.','The identifier on the front side is the same for all counterfeit banknotes - the number is 81.\r%NL%* WARNING: You should not rely only on the identifiers on the front and reverse sides if suspected of counterfeit note. You should carefully check and other security features.'),(38,3,'Special protection',43,5,94,46,NULL,NULL,NU