жа микротекст. За разлика от оригинала, нишката не флуоресцира в светло-синьо под ултравиолетова светлина, а се вижда като черна линия (от лицевата страна).'),(235,4,'Microtext 1',264,89,297,112,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'f506o4.jpg','f506f4.jpg','Microtext 1\r%NL%\r%NL%Латинският текст \"E PLURIBUS UNUM\" отпечатан с микробукви се намира под изображението на орела в големия печат на САЩ вдясно от портрета, а между колоните в печата е вмъкнат микротекст \"USA\".','Microtext 1\r%NL%\r%NL%Има следи от текст на съответните места, но не е четлив.'),(235,5,'Microtext 2',5,83,28,112,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'f506o5.jpg','f506f5.jpg','Microtext 2\r%NL%\r%NL%Думите \"FIVE DOLLARS\" отпечатни с микросимволи са вмъкнати в орнаментите на бордюра в лявия и десния край на лицевата страна на банкнотата.','Microtext 2\r%NL%\r%NL%Microtextовете в бордюрите са имитирани добре, ясни и четливи са.'),(235,6,'Microtext 3',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,382,150,413,169,'f506o6.jpg','f506f6.jpg','Microtext 3:\r%NL%\r%NL%Върху обратната страна на банкнотата - в по-ниския край на голямото виолетово число на номинала 5 са отпечатани с микротекст в негатив 2 пъти думите \"USA FIVE\". ','Microtext 3:\r%NL%\r%NL%Ясен и четлив микротекст.'),(235,8,'UV feature - front ',4,136,157,173,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'f506o8.jpg','f508f_8.jpg','Флуоресценция - лицева страна\r%NL%\r%NL%Под ултравиолетова светлина се наблюдава синя флуоресенция на осигурителната нишка - и от двете страни на банкнотата.','Флуоресценция - лицева страна\r%NL%\r%NL%Водните знаци стават видими при осветяване с UV лъчи - този вляво от центъра (трите цифри 5) се вижда в светъл цвят, а водният знак вдясно (голямо число 5) се вижда като тъмна фигура. Осигурителната нишка се появява като тъмна ивица.'),(235,9,'UV feature - back',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,5,9,149,70,'f506o9.jpg','f508f_9.jpg','Флуоресценция - обратна страна\r%NL%\r%NL%Под ултравиолетова светлина се наблюдава синя флуоресенция на осигурителната нишка - и от двете страни на банкнотата.','Флуоресценция - обратна страна\r%NL%\r%NL%Осигурителната нишка не флуоресцира. Видими са имитираните водни знаци - в светъл цвят са трите малки числа 5, а в тъмен цвят - единичното голямо число 5 (вж.вляво).'),(235,7,'Print Quality ',309,85,364,109,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'f508o_7.jpg','f508f_7.jpg','Прецизност на печата\r%NL%\r%NL%Детайли на изображенията.','Прецизност на печата\r%NL%\r%NL%Фалшивата банкнота не е така прецизна в детайлите на изображенията както оригинала, което се забелязва при наблюдение под лупа.'),(236,4,'Microtext',32,154,112,187,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c-1h06o4.jpg','c-1h06f4.jpg','Microtext\r%NL%\r%NL%Ясен и четлив под увеличително стъкло текст, отпечатан с микрошрифт - в яката на дрехата от портрета и в числото на номинала 100 в левия долен край на лицевата страна.','Microtext\r%NL%\r%NL%Microtextът интегриран в яката на дрехата и в числато на номинала 100 долу вляво НЕ е четлив.'),(236,5,'Print Quality ',321,66,359,115,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c-1h06o5.jpg','c-1h06f5.jpg','Отпечатване\r%NL%\r%NL%Плътен и равномерен цвят - чрез печатна преса.','Отпечатване\r%NL%\r%NL%Вследствие на метода на отпечатването се забелязват малки точици в зеленото на печата и в бордюрите.'),(236,2,'Security thread',100,61,118,122,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c-1h2o.jpg','c-1h06f2.jpg','Security thread\r%NL%\r%NL%Лентичка с микротекст имплантирана в хартията, видима срещу светлина.\r%NL%Под ултравиолетова светлина свети в розово/червеникаво и от двете страни на банкнотата.','Security thread\r%NL%\r%NL%Имитирана чрез отпечатване върху гърба на банкнотата. Мини-текстът върху нея също е имитиран и е четлив. Под UV светлина НЕ се наблюдава розово-червеникавата флуоресценция.'),(236,6,'UV feature - front ',258,4,453,50,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'f1h_o5.jpg','c-1h06f6.jpg','UV защита - лицева страна\r%NL%\r%NL%Банкнотата остава тъмна под ултравиолетова светлина. Осигурителната нишка показва бледо-червена (розова) флуоресценция.','UV защита - лицева страна\r%NL%\r%NL%Хартията е неактивна - не флуоресцира под ултравиолетова светлина. За разлика от оригинала, осигурителната нишка не свети в розово/червено.'),(236,7,'UV feature - back',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,291,4,455,63,'f1h_o6.jpg','c-1h067.jpg','UV защита - обратна страна\r%NL%\r%NL%Банкнотата остава тъмна под ултравиолетова светлина. Осигурителната нишка показва бледо-червена (розова) флуоресценция.','UV защита - обратна страна\r%NL%\r%NL%Хартията е неактивна - не флуоресцира под ултравиолетова светлина. За разлика от оригинала, осигурителната нишка не флуоресцира в розово-червено.'),(236,1,'Watermark',383,65,434,114,29,63,84,123,'f-1h96o1.jpg','c-1h06f1.jpg','Воден знак\r%NL%\r%NL%Полутоново изображение на портрета от банкнотата, имплантиран в хартията, видим ясно срещу проникваща светлина.','Воден знак\r%NL%\r%NL%Имитиран е чрез печат върху обратната страна на банкнотата. Образът е съставен от отпечатани нагъсто малки точици, които се виждат при наблюдение под лупа срещу светлина. '),(236,3,'Color-changing ink',353,135,434,162,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'f-1h96o4.jpg','c-1h06f3.jpg','Променящо цвета си мастило:\r%NL%\r%NL%Числото 100 в долния десен край от лицевата страна е отпечатано с променящо цвета си мастило. При разглеждане вертикално то е зелено, но става тъмно-синьо до черно, когато се погледне под ъгъл.','Променящо цвета си мастило\r%NL%\r%NL%Числото 100 е отпечатано първо с черно мастило. После върху него е насложено зелено блестящо мастило (не е много прецизно - някъде излиза от контурите на числото). При наклоняване на банкнотата черният цвят доминира (зеленото прозира), което имитира оптически вариращ ефект. '),(237,2,'Security thread',185,10,198,200,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c-1ho2.jpg','c-20f2.jpg','Security thread\r%NL%\r%NL%Built-in paper strip, visible when looking against the light and contains negative microprint \"Euro\" and the nominal value of the banknote 20.','Security thread\r%NL%\r%NL%The security thread has been imitated by means of printing on the front of the note. The microtext on the thread is legible. '),(237,9,'Fluorescence - back side',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,260,190,406,240,'c20_o8.jpg','c-20f9.jpg','Fluorescence - back side\r%NL%\r%NL%In additionof the fluorescent fibers, under ultraviolet light it is observed fluorescence in yellow the numbers on the nominal, the name of the currency, the map of Europe and the bridges.','Fluorescence - back side\r%NL%\r%NL%As the paper is optically active it becomes bright under ultraviolet light. The fluorescent fibres and ink have not been imitated.'),(237,3,'Holographic stripe',402,5,440,220,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c-20o3.jpg','c-20f3.jpg','Holographic strip\r%NL%\r%NL%When changing the angle of observation the images of the euro symbol and the face value of the banknote alternate.\r%NL%In monitoring against the light microscopic holes can be seen forming the Euro-logo.','Holographic strip\r%NL%\r%NL%Липсват детайлите и оптичните ефекти на оригиналната холограма. Деметализираното (перфорираното) евро-лого не е имитирано.'),(237,4,'See-through register',1,2,41,49,410,2,455,52,'c20-o4.jpg','c-20f4.jpg','See-through register\r%NL%\r%NL%A see-through register is a security feature which is partly printed on the front and partly on the reverse side of a document. In transmitted light both parts must combine seamlessly to give a complete picture.','See-through register\r%NL%\r%NL%Отделните сегменти не си пасват съвсем точно, което се забелязва ясно при наблюдение срещу светлина.'),(237,8,'Fluorescence - front side',215,164,360,220,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c20o6.jpg','c-20f8.jpg','Fluorescence - front side\r%NL%\r%NL%Фибрите в хартията флуоресцират в червено, синьо и зелено. Освен това се наблюдава и флуоресценция на определени елементи от дизайна в зелен и оранжев цвят. Хартията като цяло остава тъмна.','Fluorescence - front side\r%NL%\r%NL%Тъй като хартията е оптически активна, под ултравиолетова светлина става светла. Флуоресциращите мастила и фибрите не са имитирани.'),(237,7,'Microtextове',65,216,99,240,15,50,47,78,'c-20o7.jpg','c-20f7.jpg','Microprints\r%NL%\r%NL%Very small print (smaller than 0,5 mm) which can only be read clearly with a magnifying glass.','Microtextове\r%NL%\r%NL%Нечетливи.'),(237,1,'Watermark',12,69,80,160,380,70,445,155,'f20_o1.jpg','c-20f1.jpg','Watermark\r%NL%\r%NL%Implanted in the paper halftone image of an architectural motif that is clearly visible when observed against the penetrating light. Below it is visible contrast watermark - the number of the nominal 20.','Watermark\r%NL%\r%NL%Имитацията е постигната чрез отпечатване и от двете страни на банкнотата. При наблюдение срещу светлина той е слабо видим.\r%NL%'),(237,5,'ISARD код',240,15,265,65,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'f20_o3.jpg','c-20f5.jpg','ISARD код\r%NL%\r%NL%Test for authenticity by scratching with a fingernail - feels the relief of subtle parallel lines, from which is shaped the graphic element.','ISARD код\r%NL%\r%NL%Имитиран е чрез щамповане - натиск върху обратната страна и е постигнат слаб релеф.'),(237,6,'Iridescent strip',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,180,5,225,240,'f20_o6.jpg','c-20f6.jpg','Iridescent strip\r%NL%\r%NL%Viewed at an angle under bright light it has a silvery-gold color and it is transparent. The euro symbol and the face value of the banknote can be seen on it.','Iridescent strip\r%NL%\r%NL%Imitated iridescent strip is pretty shiny and thick.\r%NL%The strip has no transparency and golden-yellow color to that in the authentic bill. '),(238,2,'Security thread',206,4,226,222,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c50-o2.jpg','f-50c2f.jpg','Security thread\r%NL%\r%NL%It is implanted in the paper, a negative mini-text is imprinted on it. \r%NL%Becomes visible against penetrating light.','Security thread\r%NL%\r%NL%The imitated thread is interposed between two layers of paper. The microtext is barely visible.'),(238,3,'See-through register',3,4,42,44,410,3,450,44,'c50-o6.jpg','f-50c3f.jpg','See-through register\r%NL%\r%NL%The elements of the number \"50\" printed onto the front and back of the banknote perfectly match.','See-through register\r%NL%\r%NL%Individual elements of the number \"50\" do not fit exactly. It can be clearly seen the misalignment when viewing against penetrating light.'),(238,5,'Color-changing ink',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,373,196,445,245,'cf50o4.jpg','f-50c5f.jpg','Color-changing ink\r%NL%\r%NL%When changing the angle of observation the number of the nominal changes its color from violet to olive green and brown.','Color-changing ink\r%NL%\r%NL%OVI has not been imitated, but the ink used to print the number 50 in the lower right corner of the reverse side has a certain brilliance that gives the illusion of a slight change in the color when tilting the the banknote.'),(238,4,'Hologram',380,130,445,200,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'f5002_o3.jpg','f-50c4f.jpg','Hologram\r%NL%\r%NL%When changing the viewing angle on the hologram _ alternate images of the architectural motif and the value numeral. The colors gradate.','Hologram\r%NL%\r%NL%There missing the details and the optical effects of the authentic hologram.'),(238,6,'Microtext - front side',265,48,295,81,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'f-50c6o.jpg','f-50c6f.jpg','Microtext - front side \r%NL%\r%NL%Clear and legible under a magnifying glass.','Microtext - front side\r%NL%\r%NL%Good imitation. Legible microtext.'),(238,7,'Microtext - reverse side',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,155,232,200,255,'f-50c7o.jpg','f-50c7f.jpg','Microtext - reverse side\r%NL%\r%NL%Clear and legible under a magnifying glass.','Microtext - reverse side\r%NL%\r%NL%The microtexts on the reverse side are legible (those below the bridge), but is missing that in the lower edge of the banknote left of the the middle, below the images of the islands. '),(238,1,'Watermark',6,72,82,161,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'f50-o1.jpg','f-50c1f.jpg','Watermark\r%NL%\r%NL%During observation against the light is clearly visible a halftone three-dimensional image of a part of the architectural motif from the composition on the face side and a contrast number of the nominal of the note 50 below. Under UV - light the watermark does not fluoresce.','Watermark\r%NL%\r%NL%It is imitated by means of printing on both sides of the banknote. It is barely visible against the light. Under UV raysis visible, unlike the original.'),(238,8,'Fluorescence - front side',230,90,350,190,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'f50-o7.jpg','f-50c8f.jpg','Fluorescence - front side\r%NL%\r%NL%Fluorescing in red, blue and green fibers, fluorescent design elements in different colors.','Fluorescence - front side\r%NL%\r%NL%The background remains dark (if no damage at the surface layer of the paper), but fluorescent inks are not counterfeited. Fluorescent fibers are also missing. The outlines of the watermark are visible.'),(238,9,'Fluorescence - back side',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2,4,153,76,'f50-o8.jpg','f-50c9f.jpg','Fluorescence - back side\r%NL%\r%NL%In addition of the fluorescent fibers, a fluorescence in yellow is observed also at  the numbers of nominal, the name of the currency, the map of Europe and the bridges. ','Fluorescence - back side\r%NL%\r%NL%The background remains dark (if no damage at the surface layer of the paper), but fluorescent inks are not counterfeited. Fluorescent fibers are also missing. The contours of the watermark are visible.'),(239,2,'Security thread',200,1,220,230,235,1,250,230,'c_1ho2.jpg','c_1hf2.jpg','Security thread\r%NL%\r%NL%It is implanted in the paper, contains a printed in negative mini-text.\r%NL%Does not react to ultraviolet light.','Security thread\r%NL%\r%NL%An imitation by means of printing on the obverse. The microtext on the strip is clear and legible. Under a ultraviolet light is visible as a gray stripe in contrast to the original, that is not visible.'),(239,3,'Hologram',385,136,445,206,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c_1ho3.jpg','c_1hf3.jpg','Hologram:\r%NL%\r%NL%When changing the angle of observation the images on the architectural motive and the value numeral alternate.','Hologram:\r%NL%\r%NL%The imitation is achieved by means of  foil-printing. Missing the details and the optical effects of the authentic but here the number \"100\" and the architectural motif in the middle are imitated. '),(239,4,'See-through register',9,2,55,42,390,1,446,38,'c_1ho4.jpg','c_1hf4.jpg','See-through register\r%NL%\r%NL%The separate fragments of the number of the nominal 100 printed on the front and back of the note are combined perfectly without discrepancies.','See-through register\r%NL%\r%NL%The separate elements of the number of the nominal value 100 almost completely fit in monitoring against penetrating light.'),(239,6,'Microtext',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,131,42,165,77,'c_1ho6.jpg','c_1hf6.jpg','Microtext\r%NL%\r%NL%Clear and legible under a magnifying glass microtext at different locations on the face and the reverse of the banknote.','Microtext\r%NL%\r%NL%Добра имитация - всички Microtextове са четливи под лупа.'),(239,1,'Watermark',7,52,86,178,370,44,440,155,'c1ho1.jpg','c_1hf1.jpg','Watermark\r%NL%\r%NL%A halftone image of an architectural motif and a contrast number of the nominal value below. They are implanted in the paper and are visible when are held against the light. Under ultraviolet light are not visible.','Watermark\r%NL%\r%NL%The watermark is imitated by means of printing on the obverse. Under ultraviolet light is invisible as the original. '),(239,8,'UV reverse side',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2,190,191,250,'c1ho10.jpg','c_1hf8.jpg','UV - reverse side\r%NL%\r%NL%In addition to the fibers, implanted in the paper, the numbers of par value - above and below, the name of the currency, the map of Europe and the bridges fluoresce too. ','UV - reverse side\r%NL%\r%NL%The fluorescence is well imitated.'),(239,7,'UV face side',9,200,141,250,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c1ho9.jpg','c_1hf7.jpg','UV - face side\r%NL%\r%NL%The elements printed with blue ink fluoresce green and the yellow elements glow in orange. \r%NL%The European flag and the signature of the President of the European Central Bank are green, and the stars in the flag are orange. There are visible and the fluorescent fibers too.','UV - face side\r%NL%\r%NL%The fluorescence is well imitated. The yellow stars in the European flag are orange and the signature becomes yellow-green, as in the original.'),(239,5,'Color-changing ink/OVI',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,370,200,440,250,'f_1h8-o.jpg','c_1hf5.jpg','Color-changing ink\r%NL%\r%NL%When changing the angle of observation the number of the nominal value changes its color between violet, brown and dark green.','Color-changing ink\r%NL%\r%NL%The inks used to print this number indicates a slight change in the color at change in the slope, but this is rather due to its luster.  '),(240,2,'Security thread',200,1,220,230,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c_1ho2.jpg','c-1h-f2.jpg','Security thread:\r%NL%\r%NL%It is implanted in the paper, contains microtext printed in negative.\r%NL%It does not react to ultraviolet light.','Security thread:\r%NL%\r%NL%It is imitated by means of printing on the obverse. The microtext on it is unreadable. Under a UV light from the front side a dark line was observed (as opposed to the original).'),(240,3,'Hologram',385,130,445,200,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c_1ho3.jpg','c-1h-f3.jpg','Hologram\r%NL%\r%NL%When changing the angle of observation the images of the architectural motive (gate) and the nominal value of the banknote alternate.','Hologram\r%NL%\r%NL%An imitation by means of  foil-printing. Missing the details and the optical effects of the original hologram. The image of the gate is missing, appears only number 100.'),(240,4,'See-through register',1,1,51,47,390,1,445,38,'c_1ho4.jpg','c-1h-f4.jpg','See-through register\r%NL%\r%NL%The separate fragments of the number of the nominal 100 printed on the front and back of the note are combined perfectly without discrepancies.','See-through register\r%NL%\r%NL%When observing against a penetrating light is clearly visible a discrepancy between the individual segments of the figure. '),(240,1,'Watermark',9,54,94,170,370,44,440,155,'c1ho1.jpg','c-1h-f1.jpg','Watermark\r%NL%\r%NL%A halftone image of an architectural motif and a contrast number of the nominal value below. They are implanted in the paper and are visible when the note is held against the light. Under ultraviolet light are not visible.','Watermark\r%NL%\r%NL%The image is printed on the obverse of the banknote. Under a UV light becomes visible in contrast to the original. \r%NL%The watermark - barcode also has been imitated.'),(240,9,'Fluorescence - back side',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,5,200,165,250,'c1ho10.jpg','c-1h-f9.jpg','Fluorescence - back side\r%NL%\r%NL%In addition to the fibers, implanted in the paper, the numbers of par value - above and below, the name of the currency, the map of Europe and the bridges fluoresce too. ','Fluorescence - back side\r%NL%\r%NL%It is not imitated! The paper remains dark.\r%NL%'),(240,6,'Microtext',295,50,340,78,218,65,264,90,'c-1h-o6.jpg','c-1h-f6.jpg','Microtext\r%NL%\r%NL%All microtexts are contrasting, clear and legible under a magnifying glass.','Microtext\r%NL%\r%NL%Illegible texts (also under a magnifying glass) - on both sides of the banknote.'),(240,7,'Signature',124,10,220,42,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c-1h-o7.jpg','c-1h-f7.jpg','Signature\r%NL%\r%NL%The signature of the President of the European Central Bank is clear and contrasting.','Signature\r%NL%\r%NL%The signature is blurry.\r%NL%\r%NL%'),(240,8,'Fluorescence - front side',2,200,149,250,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c1ho9.jpg','c-1h-f8.jpg','Fluorescence - front side\r%NL%\r%NL%The elements printed with blue ink fluoresce green and the yellow elements glow in orange. \r%NL%The European flag and the signature of the President of the European Central Bank are green, and the stars in the flag are orange. There are visible and the fluorescent fibers too.','Fluorescence - front side\r%NL%\r%NL%The fluorescence is achieved in some places using a special yellow ink. The edges of the elements of the number 100 from  the see-through register (upper left corner) also show a faint yellow 