xt\r%NL%\r%NL%It is imitated in the right places, but it is not legible.'),(243,7,'Fluorescence face side',229,166,416,240,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c20_o7.jpg','c.20f7.jpg','Fluorescence face side:\r%NL%\r%NL%The fibers in the paper fluoresce red, blue and green. Furthermore, it  is observed fluorescence of certain design elements in green and orange. The paper as a whole remains dark.','Fluorescence face side:\r%NL%\r%NL%The paper shows the optical activity (all is lit, unlike the back). Fluorescent the fibers miss. Yellow-green fluorescence is imitated. Orange (the stars in the flag) is missing.'),(243,4,'Iridescent strip',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,175,10,220,210,'c20-o7.jpg','c.20f4.jpg','Iridescent strip\r%NL%\r%NL%Viewed at an angle under bright light it has a silvery-gold color. On it you can see the euro symbol and the nominal value of the banknote.','Iridescent strip\r%NL%\r%NL%It is imitated, but it has low quality, it is difficult to discern.'),(243,8,'Fluorescence reverse side',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,228,3,406,48,'f20_o8.jpg','c.20f8.jpg','Fluorescence - back side:\r%NL%\r%NL%In additionof the fluorescent fibers, under ultraviolet light is observed fluorescence in yellow the numbers on the nominal, the name of the currency, the map of Europe and the bridges.','Fluorescence - back side:\r%NL%\r%NL%There is optically inactive layer with a coating to the entire surface is not lit. Fluorescent fibers miss. It is imitated yellow fluorescence of the respective elements, but there are also  lines of the barcode noticeable and printed watermark is clearly visible\n.'),(244,4,'Microtext',83,159,111,195,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c_1h96o4.jpg','c_1h964.jpg','Microtext\r%NL%\r%NL%Ясен, контрастен, четлив под лупа текст.','Microtext:\r%NL%\r%NL%Microtextът в яката (от портрета) и този, запълващ числото на номинала 100 в левия долен ъгъл на лицевата страна са ясни и четливи.'),(244,5,'Print Quality ',327,72,370,97,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c_1h96o5.jpg','c_1h965.jpg','Прецизност на печата\r%